headline: BofA Report: 60% of Homeowners and Prospective Buyers Uncertain About the Housing Market - A Three-Year High
summary: Uncertainty among current homeowners and prospective buyers is at a three-year high, with 60% saying they can't tell whether now is a good time to buy a home or not, compared to 48% two years ago, according to the latest Bank of America Homebuyer Insights Report (PDF), released in coordination with Bank of America Institute's latest On the move analysis.
